%p.article-content
  = "Dear #{@user.first_name.capitalize},"
%p.article-content
  We are really sorry, but this note is to confirm that your Host has had to cancel your booking.
%p.article-content
  PetHomeStay will refund your entire booking fee and will be in touch to try to find you another pet carer as soon as possible.
%p.article-content
  We understand this can be stressful, especially if at the last minute, but we will do everything we can to help.
%p.article-content
  Many thanks for your understanding and we will speak to you soon.
%p.article-content The PetHomeStay Team

%h3 Booking Details
%p.article-content
  = "Booking from #{@booking.check_in_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)} #{@booking.check_in_time.strftime("%H:%M")} to #{@booking.check_out_date.to_formatted_s(:day_and_month)} #{@booking.check_out_time.strftime("%H:%M")}"
%p.article-content
  = "Guest Name: #{@user.first_name.capitalize} #{@user.last_name.capitalize}"
%p.article-content
  = "Pet Name: #{@user.pet.name.capitalize}"
%p.article-content
  = "Host Name: #{@booking.bookee.first_name.capitalize} #{@booking.bookee.last_name.capitalize}"
%p.article-content
  = "HomeStay Title: #{@homestay.title}"
%p.article-content
  = "Total Booking Fee: $#{@booking.subtotal}"